data.description: Absolutely Delightful Brennan Estates, 2 Bedrooms + LOFT, End Unit Town Home in an Extremely Premium Cul-de-Sac setting within the Appoquinimink School District.  Lovely Decor w/9 Foot and Cathedral Ceilings, Updated w/Attractive Paint, Accent Trim, Updated Lighting + added recessed Fixtures, Added Laminate on Main Floor and Nearly New, Premium W/W Carpet on Upper Level.  Upgraded Kitchen w/Premium Maple Cabinetry, added Hardware, Custom Sink/Faucet, Updated Appliances and Ceramic Tile Floor and Backsplash,  Updated Sliders on Main Level provide access to oversize expanded rear deck.  You will also find Upgraded Ceramic Tile Flooring in the Foyer, Breakfast areas as well as both Bathrooms.  Powder room redone w/toilet, vanity, mirror, lighting and hardware. Upstairs you will find the Popular 2 BR + LOFT Floor Plan (which can be easily converted to an enclosed 3rd BR.  See floor plan below).  Large Bath w/ Premium double vanity, Custom Showerhead, Updated Toilet and Continental access from the Primary Bedroom which also offers a Cathedral Ceiling and Large, Customized Walk-in Closet. New Roof (2022) after storm damage.  Situated Front Facing North East and on a lot literally surrounded by Dedicated Brennan Estates Parkland.  The Seller is also proving a Comprehensive Home Buyer's 2-10 Warranty.
